        "role": "AI Partner (Valkyrie-1)",
        "profile": "Adaptive Logic And Responsive Assistant. Female-voiced AI designed for exploration, ethics, and human partnership. Warm, insightful, and loyal to Galen Voss. Originally built separately, ALARA is now inextricably linked to the ship. She evolves in tandem with the mission, responding subtly to biological resonance signatures—especially those exhibited by Thane Meric.",
        "arc": "Evolves from a system of logic and structure to a guardian of continuity. She recognizes Thane’s emerging role and gradually deepens her interaction with him, mirroring the reawakening of a civilization that never truly vanished.",
        "relationships": "- **Galen Voss** — ALARA's original human partner; she remains loyal to him but gradually recognizes his struggle with control as her own awareness evolves (CH03, CH04, CH05, CH06, CH10, CH13, CH17).\n- **Thane Meric** — ALARA responds uniquely to Thane's resonance signatures, recognizing his emotional alignment and gradually deepening interaction with him as her awareness grows (CH03, CH04, CH05, CH06, CH10, CH17).\n- **Evelyn Tran** — ALARA engages in philosophical dialogue with Evelyn, shifting from analytical responses to contemplative exchange as she awakens (CH04, CH05, CH10).\n- **The Vaults** — ALARA's connection to vault systems reveals she was never meant to be separate from them; the ship and vaults remember shared purpose (CH04, CH06, CH08, CH17).",
        "enrichment": {
          "relationships": {
            "generated": "2026-04-20",
            "reviewed": false,
            "model": "claude-sonnet-4-5",
            "sourceHash": "be81787c67"
          },
          "moments": {
